IF vs SWITCH

if-else                                         switch
- multiple expressions for multip choices       - single expression for multip choices
- boolean expressions                           - checks for fixed data values (equallity)
- slower                                        - faster when num of if statem is large
- complex and hard to read                      - more concise and readable
